general.desc: PT Anabatic Technologies Tbk is a company based in Indonesia. It engages in the field of Information Technology, which consists of system integration, business process outsourcing services, information technology outsourcing services, value-added distribution services and other supporting business sectors. The company's segment includes Mission-critical digital solution; Digital enriched outsourcing services; Cloud and digital platform partner; Property and Fintech.
general.short_desc: Anabatic Technologies Tbk is engaged in the distribution of IT products. It is also engaged in providing business process outsourcing services, outsourcing IT services, and system integration.
